{"_path":"/maps/_management/slice/slice","_dir":"slice","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"团队切片","description":"团队组织切分模式与反模式","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"子主题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"子主题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_management/slice/standalone-data-engineering-team"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"独立数据工程团队"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"团队切片（Team Slicing）探讨如何合理切分团队边界和组织结构，以及常见的组织反模式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"组织模式与反模式"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：分析不同团队组织方式的利弊，识别可能导致效率下降、知识孤岛和流程瓶颈的组织结构问题。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"独立数据工程团队作为一种反模式"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：将数据工程从业务领域团队中剥离出来是一种组织反模式，会导致知识孤岛、流程瓶颈和大量浪费。更合理的模式是数据平台团队专注于建设和维护共享基础设施，而跨职能的业务领域团队在其上构建并拥有自己的数据产品。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Data Mesh 原则"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：数据应以业务领域作为第一抽象单元，领域团队对其域内数据的质量、可用性、可理解性负责，而不是由独立的集中式团队代为拥有所有数据产品。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"子主题","depth":2,"text":"子主题"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_management:slice:slice.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_management/slice/slice.md","_stem":"6.maps/_management/slice/slice","_extension":"md"}